summary: my anime only self while surfing the mha/bnha fandom: like is this fanon or is this a spoiler from the manga ok too many people...
body:
my anime only self while surfing the mha/bnha fandom: like is this fanon or is this a spoiler from the manga

ok too many people are repeating it so maybe it is something from the manga

nope apparently the fandom has decided this is going to be a thing

also this fanfic/concept/au is popular enough to get enough fanart that it is hard to tell what is canon and fanon

if enough people speculate something that then becomes correct is it fanon or is it spoilers? let’s assume all discussion is fanon speculation

let’s assume everything is fanon until otherwise noted

okay that seems like a character i havent met yet okay let’s just keep scrolling
